Speaker of the House of Representatives, Femi Gbajabiamila has inaugurated three House ad hoc committees. The ceremony held at Room 414 of the House of Representatives wing of the National Assembly complex. In attendance were lawmakers from the various political parties. The three ad hoc committees would manage the affairs of the House, pending the constitution of standing committees. They are House ad hoc committees on Media, Welfare, and Selection. Reps inaugurate ad hoc committees, adjourn till July 2 N/Assembly adjourns plenary for office, seat allocations Dogara raises House committees to 95 Dear Esteemed reader, As part of our drive to keep improving the content of our newspaper, we are conducting a readership survey to enable us serve you better. Kindly take two minutes of your time to fill in this questionnaire. Thank you for your time. Click here to begin